::Savanna::

She nodded to Kluster. "Of that I have no doubt." She wasn't 
nervouse, she was in the comapny of strange bots who had not aquired 
her trust yet.  She could smell the Pred on Phobia.  She cursed 
herself for thinking that it would be a maximal who landed.  She 
cursed again at herself for letting herself make a stupid assumetion.
She watched and listened to the others as they talked.
